---
title: Chicken Sausage Tortelloni with Mushrooms, Italian Cheese Blend & Fresh Parsley
description: This delicious bowl of pasta is the total package! Our chefs paired these comforting cheese-stuffed pasta with mushrooms and tossed it all together in a rich tomato sauce to deliver an extra-tender bite and a huge amount of flavor. Shower your tortelloni with a melty Italian cheese blend and fresh parsley before serving for the perfect weeknight dinner idea—ready to enjoy in just 15 minutes.
